reviewText: This is a very disturbing video.  It is not quite up to the quality of THE NEW CLINTON CHRONICLES, but contains material not included in that video.  Strongly recommend this video for anyone researching the history of the Clintons and even remotely considering voting for Hillary for president.  Please do your research before voting. For additional history of the Clinton's see SIEGE AT RUBY RIDGE and WACO-A NEW REVELATION which are excellent historical documentaries.  Also if you are able to find it on the internet, JANET RENO EXPOSED by Jack Thompson is very disturbing. INNOCENTS BETRAYED is excellent background history of Nazi confiscation of guns for those undecided about current efforts by our government to take guns away from us.
